<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink221">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi kātalar</l>
<l>pāvai yaṉṉaveṉ ṉāykaviṉ ṟolaiya</l>
<l>naṉmā mēṉi pacappac</l>
<l>celva leṉpatam malaikeḻu nāṭē</l>
</lg> 
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en"> 
<l>  Alas, O friend, </l>
<l>“I shall leave,” my lover says, </l>
<l>“for [my] town with mountains,”</l>
<l>as my doll-like fading beauty [further] wanes, </l>
<l>and good dark body fades. </l>

</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
